HOW_TO_MAKE_A_TUTU_DRESS_WITHIN 2 HOURS_FOR_YOUR_BELOVED_BABY_GIRL ?
Workshop schedule : Saturday , 29st Nov 2014
Duration : 2 hours ( from 3pm - 5pm )
Location : Uprising_Saigon , 420/6 Le_Van_Sy , Ward 14 , Dist 3
Ticket fee : 300,000 vnd
< < Pls inbox your address so that we deliver ticket to door for you > >
Number of attendance : 10
Description :
This workshop is about instructing you to make a simple dress by hand for your baby girl by very simple materials that you can find easily in your nearby market . Just only few basic steps , you can creative a fantastic dress for your baby girl .
Why should you join to this workshop ?
- We do not only instruct you to make a dress , but we also want to creative a “ mommy community ” so that people can learn and share hobbies and experience each other .
- Our well experience instructor who works in fashion and garment industry will company you during the workshop , so you can save your cost by making wrong if you make alone
- We support materials that are much cheaper than buying in market yourself
Let ’ s come to have some fun and some new experience with us . Nothing special than making a dress for your baby girl by yourself .
